Question 1:
Write a playbook which installs the vsftpd package on all the machines.

Question 2:
Write a playbook which enables the ftp service in firewalld.

Question 3:
Write a playbook which writes "Welcome to Ansible." in the index.html created using the ad-hoc command.

Question 4:
